# Abstract describing the software
abstract: >
  FoxML Core is a machine-learning infrastructure stack for cross-sectional and panel data,
  providing config-driven ML pipeline architecture with leakage detection, reproducibility tracking,
  and multi-model training systems. Designed for ML infrastructure teams, data scientists, and researchers
  working with temporal panel data.

